From afc774996c54e115fecddd86ad052ee842b1e6c6 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Mon, 29 Jun 2026 12:58:19 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 10/18] fix(P2a): unifier l'indicateur LIVE sur #ff6d2e
 (charter live orange)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- 53 occurrences #ff4d4d → #ff1744 (charter danger) pour contextes alertes/erreurs
- 12 occurrences LIVE contextuelles → #ff6d2e (charter live):
  * .badge-live, .lt5-title, .lt5-score, .ld-score
  * .match-tab.live-tab.active, .live-count-badge
  * tr.tennis-vb-row.is-live, .tn-live-ind
  * .tn-live-tag, .tn-live-tag i
  * .tvb-pred-kpi.live, .tennis-status-live
- 24 occurrences #FF6B00 (CS2 blocs) → #ff6d2e
- --tn2-live: #ef4444 → #ff6d2e

Référence: audit/pariscore/frontend/src/styles/tokens.css (--color-live: #ff6d2e)
